    "AI利用券は端末に安全に保管されますが、端末が壊れたりアプリを削除すると失われます。貯めずに早めにお使いください": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "AI tickets are safely stored on this device, but they will be lost if the device is damaged or you delete the app. Please use them soon."
